Class SetConstraint<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.cq.social.ugc.api.AbstractConstraint
      • com.adobe.cq.social.ugc.api.AbstractPropertyConstraint
        • com.adobe.cq.social.ugc.api.SetConstraint<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of objects in the set.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint

    public class SetConstraint<T>
extends AbstractPropertyConstraint
implements Constraint
    SetConstraint is a property constraint which restricts the value of a property to one of a set of values.
